LOCUS       SpyTag                    13 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  SpyTag — 13-aa peptide (AHIVMVDAYKPTK) from the CnaB2 domain of S.
            pyogenes FbaB that forms a spontaneous, irreversible isopeptide bond
            to its protein partner SpyCatcher..
